descriptionHtml:
Marissa was made by me only and i take full credit for making the save file. However i used resources to make it. See Credits

Marissa is a lost stranger that doesn\'t know she\'s dragonborn. Yea... that\'s pretty much it.

You can get the ears at:
http://www.mediafire.com/?641j7a0b8cvxa29 - This file does NOT belong to me and i use it only because i cannot find the uploader. BUT i do know that the items in that file are made by Tona a mod maker from oblivion.

Great to use with Coverwomen by mrLenski - Look 1
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563
And CoverEyes also by mrLenski
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=4869

If you want anymore pictures or save files just pm me.

Hope you Enjoy!

By the way if you don\'t like something about the way she looks or have a hair mod just hit the \"~\" button and type    showracemenu       and you can edit her to your liking.
author: MrFarc661
